('b84f79ad-2ce7-5c59-8216-1ea54e0f92ac', '6ba8bebb-72f7-41c5-ae30-b931d133d6d2', 'He wants to ___ to the park.', '他想要去公園。', 'go', 'stay', 'cook', 'sleep', 'go 表示「去」或是「走」。', 'Go → 去/走'),
('348c8871-531a-5a81-97c1-df8c84c28588', '527aeca3-cf9d-4fbc-987d-67a0bd2dd649', 'We ___ not want to miss the opportunity to study abroad.', '我們不想錯過出國留學的機會。', 'do', 'are', 'have', 'were', 'do 與 not 結合構成否定句。', 'do not (don''t) 表示否定。'),
('322d4c9a-066d-5f27-8ee9-cd53d10e21e4', 'bdf62229-5b97-4ca6-b357-8e0d6aac7c03', '___ are the winners, so please come up to the stage to collect your prize.', '你們是贏家，所以請上台領取你們的獎品。', 'you', 'they', 'we', 'he', 'you 為代名詞，此處指複數的你們。', 'you 就像是指著一群人說「你們」。'),
('a990324a-3c3b-57d5-97de-064f6e90ef04', 'c65a0c33-e9b1-448a-98db-bb934683f81c', 'I like apples, ___ I don''t like bananas.', '我喜歡蘋果，但是我不喜歡香蕉。', 'but', 'and', 'so', 'or', '表示轉折 (但是)', '看到 but 就要想到轉折 (轉折 → but)');
